@page "/"
@page "/MegaMenu/"
@page "/MegaMenuWA/"
@page "/MegaMenu360/"

<div class="container py-5">
    <div class="text-center mb-4">
        <h3 class="fw-bold text-primary">
            MegaMenu360 – Dynamic JSON-Based Mega Menu for Blazor
        </h3>
    </div>

    <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-lg-8">
            <p class="lead">
                <strong>MegaMenu360</strong> is a fully dynamic, JSON-driven mega menu
                component designed for modern Blazor applications. It provides a
                flexible multi-column layout where each menu section can display links,
                icons, badges, or even integrated images — all defined through a simple
                JSON file.
            </p>

            <p>
                The menu is built around a reusable component
                <code>NavMegaMenu360.razor</code> that automatically renders the entire
                navigation structure. Just drop in your <code>menu.json</code> file —
                no API or server calls required. The component reads your JSON data and
                constructs a responsive, visually appealing menu styled with
                <strong>Bootstrap 5</strong> and <strong>Font Awesome 6</strong>.
            </p>

            <p>
                Designed to be lightweight, isolated, and easily embeddable, MegaMenu360
                fits seamlessly into any Blazor layout. It’s the perfect foundation for
                dynamic navigation, with plans for future enhancements such as a
                real-time visual Menu Builder UI for editing JSON structures directly
                within your app.
            </p>

            <ul class="list-group list-group-flush mt-4">
                <li class="list-group-item">
                    ✅ Dynamic, file-based configuration — no API calls required
                </li>
                <li class="list-group-item">
                    ✅ Multi-column mega menu layout with image integration
                </li>
                <li class="list-group-item">
                    ✅ Styled using Bootstrap 5 and Font Awesome 6
                </li>
                <li class="list-group-item">
                    ✅ Reusable Blazor component: <code>NavMegaMenu360</code>
                </li>
                <li class="list-group-item">
                    🚧 Future-ready for integrated visual Menu Builder
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

